#. Tag: screen
#: storage_multipath.xml:4824
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&lt;Month day hh:mm:ss&gt; | Prioritizer 'weightedpath hbtl [1,3]:.:.+:.+ "
"260\n"
"[0,2]:.:.+:.+ 20' not found in /lib64/multipath"
